videos.headline: Louisville QB leads team to victory
videos.description: ESPN's college football analysts John Gregory and Jim Barbar review Louisville QB Lamar Jackson's impressive 212 yards passing and 184 yards rushing, leading the Cardinals to a 45-3 victory against Samford.
